          "captureNotes": "Academic paper formalizing spec-as-source workflows. Connects to Design by Contract. Positions vocabularies, invariants, and constraints as the 'real' system with code as a compiled by-product. First Tier A source for claim 2. LLM coding agents benefit immensely from SDD because structured specs reduce ambiguity."
        },
